# AURORA 测试规范

## 测试结构

```
tests/
├── conftest.py              # 共享 fixtures
├── test_aurora_core.py      # 核心类测试
├── test_tension.py          # 矛盾管理测试
├── test_determinism.py      # 确定性测试
├── test_idempotency.py      # 幂等性测试
├── test_components/         # 组件单元测试
├── integration/             # 集成测试
└── performance/             # 性能基准测试
```

## Fixtures 使用

在 `conftest.py` 中定义共享 fixtures：

```python
@pytest.fixture
def aurora_memory() -> AuroraMemory:
    """Fresh AuroraMemory instance for testing."""
    return AuroraMemory(
        cfg=MemoryConfig(dim=64, max_plots=100),
        seed=42
    )

@pytest.fixture
def populated_memory(aurora_memory: AuroraMemory) -> AuroraMemory:
    """Memory with some test data."""
    for i in range(10):
        aurora_memory.ingest(f"测试交互 {i}")
    return aurora_memory
```

